**UPDATE: September 8th 2011**

- Fixed one major bug
- Fixed many small bugs
- Balanced some traps
- Fixed and improved some traps

Map Details

- 26 traps (including pitfalls)
- 4 endings (old, knife, bhop and a secret ending)
- 3 flashes
- 64 spawns
- anti afk

This map is the offical update of deathrun_insomnia.
(The original creators of insomnia worked on this).

Please report any bugs or suggestions you have for a future update to this map you can add me on steam (rtsblacksoul).

thanks.
